dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Portage County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2021.Roads: [Road segments representing centerlines of all roadways in Portage County. Compiled from orthoimagery. This representation of the road centerlines support address geocoding and mapping. ROW: Polygon depiction of road right of way and access easements to be used with tax parcel maps. The polygons are broken into localized pieces to avoid annoying the Parcel Fabric gremlins.Easements are mapped where there is a mappable description available. Being mapped doesn't mean the easement is still active or open to the public.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.portage.wi.us/department/planning-zoning/land-information-gis/maps-and-gis-data
